Main Features:
•	Enabled Firebase authentication
•	Created an authentication component “authentication.component” under the authentication directory.
•	Created an authentication service to communicate with the backend “authentication.service.ts” under the authentication directory.
•	Added messages in HTML for auth component “authentication.component.html” that only appears if either an incorrect email/password is entered or if the user is trying to create an account with an already used email. 
Bonus Features:
•	Added User Model in “user.model.ts” within the authentication directory.
•	Added Firebase Authentication implemented through auth page login that brings back all of the database card components.
